headline.print_headline: Houston Texan Lineman Quessenberry Diagnosed With Lymphoma
headline.main: Houston Texan Lineman Quessenberry Diagnosed With Lymphoma

lead_paragraph: Houston Texans offensive lineman David Quessenberry, 23, was placed on the NFL's Non-Football Illness List on Tuesday after being diagnosed with lymphoma, a type of blood cancer, the team said.
